name: SingularityNET
description: With a team that has amassed AI developers and robotics scientists, SingularityNET (AGI) was developed to serve as a marketplace for AI services made accessible through the blockchain. From individual algorithms & standalone AI applications to machine learning or model training, these services would be offered to satisfy demand for AI among various communities. The long-term goals of the SingularityNET team include building an ecosystem of AI Agents that would interact with one another using resources from the OpenCog Foundation and help people to create, share, and monetize AI services at scale over a decentralized network.
